Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:05.02,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:07.73,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:12.86,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:18.03,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.75,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:39.22,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:51.07,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:54.36,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:57.11,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:01:01.99,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:07.46,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:16.80,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:25.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the ICPO...\NI am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how many suspects\Nthere are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:31.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a strong possibility\Nthey're Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:37.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, I have a pretty good idea behind\Nyour motive and why you're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you're doing is...evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:44.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I am justice!\N- What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm saving the meek that fear evil!\N- This is unreal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who will become\Nthe god of the ideal, new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:52.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:53.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I will definitely find you and finish you!\N- I will definitely find you and finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:58.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:01:59.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:01.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- justice!\N- justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, let's start with\Nthe tip-line reports first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:11.19,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(357,143)}Serial Murder\NSpecial\NInvestigations\NHeadquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:10.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, there have been\N3,029 responses
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:16.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,about the murders from\Ntelephone calls, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of them are from\Ncurious members of the public...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are fourteen people\Nwho say that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they either "know the killer"\Nor "have seen the killer."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:28.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Each account was followed up\Nand recorded carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one had information that\Nhasn't already been released to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:37.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also 21 people\Nwho claim they are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't want to rule out\Nany possibilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So all 21 people\Nwere put on record and filed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:53.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up: victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon further investigation, we have\Nconfirmed that information
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of the heart attack victims was, in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:05.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,publicly available in Japan\Nprior to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:12.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning L's request that we investigate\Nthe times of death for each victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:16.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found they occurred between 4 p.m.\Nuntil 2 a.m. on weekdays Japan's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,68% of them occurred between\N8 p.m. and 12 midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, we have\Na great variation of times
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:26.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on Saturdays, Sundays, and holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:30.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is extremely interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:36.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from those times of death...\Nthe culprit may be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have other grounds for this belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing from the fact that\Nthe perpetrator is only killing criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he's probably driven by\Nhis own idealistic sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He may even be trying\Nto become a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that he has\Na very childish mentality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a mere possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:03.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But please get rid of the stereotype\Nthat the culprit couldn't be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:09.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering various possibilities\Nis the shortest route to arresting Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue\Nyour investigative report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone else noticed anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:27.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I'm in no way saying this\Nto give credit to Kira's actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:32.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but...for the past few days, worldwide...\Nand especially in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of violent crimes more serious\Nthan robbery has dropped drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's to be expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:45.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, that about sums up\Nour investigative report for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:57.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.\NI feel as if we're closing in on the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:01.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'd like to make another request.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the teams investigating\Nthe victims, news and internet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:07.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to examine once more
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:12.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,how the victims' identities\Nwere made public in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:17.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know if pictures of\Nthe victims' faces were shown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem very tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pulling all-nighters lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What I said about crimes\Ndropping drastically...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,\Neveryone knows already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:42.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep speaking the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when it's about things people\Nhesitate to bring up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you had gone\Non to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we should commend Kira for admirably\Nreducing crime rates,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,now that might have been a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible! Support that killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did you understand any\Nof that by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it seems like Dad's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's home early!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:28.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! At least figure out\Nthe last problem by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will after dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:32.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping your little sister\Ndo her homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you sure have confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing that gives me\Nconfidence to fight the police
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if they move against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home...Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, how are your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? They're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's at the top of his grade as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my wonderful big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my wonderful son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you seem a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:20.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you any details,\Nbut this current case is very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is one of the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the reason why\Nyou're so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:37.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hack into my father's computer\Nfrom my own without leaving a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can always keep track of\Nthe investigative situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:08:01.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are beginning to\Nsuspect that the culprit is a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, doesn't that mean\Nyou're in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cause of death is written within\N40 seconds of writing the person's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cause of death is not specified,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the person will simply die\Nof a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:21.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After writing the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:27.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,details of the death should be written\Nin the next 6 minutes and 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:33.05,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,149)\frz325.746\fad(668,0)}Serial Murder\NSpecial\NInvestigation\NHeadquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if I write "heart attack"\Nas the cause of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:38.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can write down the circumstance\Nand time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:43.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I may be able to provide you\Na little bit more entertainment, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 148, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:14.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ahold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There were another\N23 heart attack victims yesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The day before, there were\Nanother 23 victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:45.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One at every hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that this has continued for\Ntwo weekdays straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Means our sketch of the culprit\Nhas become doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, anyone could skip\Nschool for two days...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:56.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It does appear less likely now\Nthat the culprit's a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the message Kira's trying\Nto send!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why one every hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are all the victims\Nin prisons,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where they can be easily be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is trying to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:19.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he can freely control...\Nthe time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:29.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we began to suspect that\NKira was a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the timing of the killings changed as\Nif to contradict our theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:37.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a coincidence?\NNo, the timing is too convenient...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that Kira knows\Nwhat the police know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is obviously\Na direct challenge from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L is probably panicking by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:57.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have fifty criminals left\Nespecially for times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:03.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, L should be starting to suspect\Nsomeone involved with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has found a way to obtain information\Nfrom the task force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot ignore this fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:20.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Kira's real objective?\NWhat is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By getting rid of the student theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you at a bigger disadvantage if\NL thinks you're connected to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in order to find L\Nand finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:43.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In human society, there are only\Na few people who actually trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true even among police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:51.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In particular, L and the police\Ndon't trust each other at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you trust someone\Nwhose name and face you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When L discovers that the findings\Nfrom the investigation were leaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:03.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he's bound to search for leads\Non me within the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:08.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he does, it's only a matter of time\Nbefore the police get really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L and the police are working\Ntogether to try to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:20.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L is investigating the police\Nand the police will start investigating L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who's\Ngoing to find L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will track him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will eliminate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.86,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(384,113)}Serial Murder\NSpecial\NInvestigations\NHeadquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.78,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz43.325\pos(299,239)}Letter of\Nresignation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, these are\Nour letters of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer us to a different case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, we will\Nquit the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Because we\Nvalue our lives, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By L's deduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:06.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira can kill people indirectly\Nthrough supernatural powers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would try to kill anyone\Nwho tried to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he'll be\Nexecuted if he gets caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:18.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, in that media stunt,\NL challenged Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:21.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Try and kill me," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But L never showed\Nhis face or revealed his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just recently, L ordered us\Nto find out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:37.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if the victims' faces and names\Nwere broadcast in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the victims were those
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whose faces were broadcast\Nto the Japanese public!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,unlike someone we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:52.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we carry around our personal identification\Nas well as our photos in our police IDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't hide our faces,\Nwe're out in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,could be killed at any time by Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why we wish to be\Nremoved from our post.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the solution to this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:25.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take x squared equals...large x.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:31.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can think of large x's\Nquadratic equation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as the multiple of two integers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We had the FBI come to Japan\Nfour days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are currently investigating\Nthe police involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the list, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:49.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 141 people within\Nthe police force alone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who have access to classified\Ninformation on the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:01.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of the 141 people\Nor someone close to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is definitely among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:09.51,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz341.123\pos(404,402)\fad(0,543)}Soichiro Yagami (48) DOB 7/12/59\NDetective Superintendent,\NNPA Head of Special Investigations\NSerial Murder Case\N\N\N\N\N\NSachiko Yagami (41) DOB 10/10/66\NHousewife\N\N\N\N\N\NLight Yagami (17) DOB 2/28/89\NHigh School Student
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you gotta second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to talk to me\Nas much as possible when we're outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll just talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your ears if\Nyou don't want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything\Nagainst you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the notebook couldn't\Nhave been picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by a better person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:36.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have to stick around with you\Nuntil the notebook is finished or you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:41.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not on your side or L's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, I knew that much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll never say\Nanything about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:53.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whether what you're doing is\Nright or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:58.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to say this\Nas your roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me\Nthis all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:11.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,not because I'm an ally of Kira,\Nbut because it's creeping me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the point already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's been following\Nyou all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't see me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:47.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because I'm always hovering behind you,\NI feel like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuk, I'll be sure to finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that L has\Nbegun to suspect the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:08.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He must need quite a large number\Nof people to investigate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:11.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he had\N50 people investigating...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:15.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no chance that\NI'd be suspected of being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:19.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should only look like\Na regular high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:25.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if I leave it alone for several months,\Nthat possibility won't remain at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must learn my tracker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I find that out,\NI can get rid of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you in on something good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two big differences\Nbetween...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami and humans\Nwho have a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:50.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Shinigami have\Nto write peoples' names in the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really talkative today, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Shinigami receive\Nthe human's remaining life span from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get their remaining life span?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say that there's a person\Nwho will live 'til 60 in the Human World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:09.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You write that he'll die\Nat forty in the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty minus forty equals twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:19.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those twenty years in the Human World\Nare added on to a Shinigami's life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we don't slack off,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:27.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if we're shot in the head\Nor stabbed in the heart with a knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, no matter how many names\Nyou write in the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your life span will not lengthen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the difference between Shinigami\Nand humans who have a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:41.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:44.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To humans, that's very kind\Nof the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:51.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our second difference is\Nof probably more interest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:55.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of lengthening life,\Nit's about cutting it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutting it short?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:04.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Shinigami sees a person's face,\Nthey know their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:06.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In a Shinigami's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:14.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a human's name and life span can\Nbe seen above a person's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Name...and life span?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, in my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:23.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see your name and\Nlife span right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:27.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I convert it to human time,\NI'll know how many years it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I wouldn't tell you even if\Nyou stretched my mouth open...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my mouth is\Nstretched out as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:42.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami never have problems\Nknowing the names of the people they kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:48.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They also know how much life\Nthey're going to receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the crucial difference\Nbetween you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:20:00.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami can also turn the eyes\Nof whoever picked up their Death Note
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,into Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:08.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But only if a deal is made, one that's\Nbeen with us since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for a Shinigami's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:20.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is half of that person's remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of my remaining life span...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:29.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you were to live another 50 years,\Nyou'll have 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was one year more,\Nyou'll have half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:36.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And since you're neither\NKira's ally nor L's,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:40.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't tell me the name of someone\NI want to kill, even if you see their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...\NI can't get your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:51.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also part of the Shinigami code.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:58.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me half your remaining life\Nand I'll give you the Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:04.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that...\NI'll know everyone's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that it'll be easier\Nto use the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, what'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:27.80,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:33.18,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:42.19,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:48.61,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:53.16,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:58.87,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:06.34,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:11.51,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:22.27,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:27.86,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm a trickster who doesn't know solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:38.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew Death Note would carry out\Neverything written in it so accurately?
